        <p class="hero-subtitle">Track real-time market data, analyze trends, and make informed investment decisions with our powerful dashboard.</p>
        
        <div class="market-cards" style=" text-decoration:none;">
            <a href="/home.BSE" style=" text-decoration:none;"0>
